	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Bump. Working on this again, lots of trouble with the PPU! $2006 is far more difficult than I anticipated since it's documented operation doesn't fit hardware very well! The logic is so convoluted, it would seem we're missing some key pieces of $2002,2005,2006's operation.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


